						<p>Why Names Matter</p>
					</div>
					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;text-align:center;"><b>The world was formed by a vibration, the vibration of the sound “OM”.<br/><sub>-Upanishad</sub></b></p>
					<!-- <p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;"><b><sub>-Upanishad</sub></b></p> -->
					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;">Have you ever wondered why spiritual leaders took up a new name from their gurus when they began their spiritual journeys? </p>
					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;">Why Narendranath Datta became Swami Vivekananda, Mukunda Lal Ghosh became Swami Yogananda, In Genesis (17:5; 17:15), Abram’s name changed to Abraham and his wife's name from Sarai to Sarah.</p>
					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;">There are many more citations of name changes across religions if you trace back history. </p>
					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;">In fact, on the birth of a child, a naming ceremony historically was considered as a religious practice, conducted with rituals by a guru who understood the power of a name.</p>
					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;"> Whatever be the method or science used, the reason was very clear and crystal<b> - everyone knew that a name through its vibration of sound had a great power to awaken a person’s true destiny, identity and help achieve success in his goals.</b></p>
					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;"> And that’s what is a <b>“Balanced Name”.</b></p>
					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;">It ensures that your purpose in life and the strengths that are gifted to you at the time of birth <b>(understood by analysing your date of birth)</b> are available to use in your life and in an enhanced way. </p>
					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;">Just like a Mantra helps you calm your mind and provide divine strength, your name works in an exactly similar way. Only that your name is your own personal mantra that you hear and relate to every day of your life.</p>
					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;"> Importantly, the effects of it condition your mind to align with the strengths of your subconscious mind, helping you achieve peace, success, and happiness in life.</p>
					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;">Similarly, with an unbalanced name, a person can live a life much restricted to his true potential and much away from his path of destiny.</p>
					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;">At NaamVidya, it is our endeavour to help you achieve the perfectly balanced name.</p>
					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;">Using the power behind the science of numbers, passed on to us by renowned teachers and guru’s, we are here to guide you in this journey of material and spiritual success.</p>
					<p style="font-family: 'Varela Round', sans-serif;">If you are interested in understanding more about the science click here to read our blog <a href="/balanced-name">“Origins of a balanced name”</a></p>
